  "title": "IT Onboarding Workshop Production",
  "slug": "agenda-onboarding",
  "categorySlug": "it-onboarding",
  "html": "<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section kb-article-row-0-padding\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-2\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h1 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">IT Onboarding Workshop Production</h1>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">This is a hands-on workshop where success criteria are to be able to start the GDPR Scanning of e-mail. </h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\"><div class=\"hs-callout-type-warning\" data-hs-callout-type=\"warning\">\n<p>If you are using Office365 you must be able to access the Global Admin for your tenant</p>\n</div>\n<h3><strong>Client Preparation/tasks before the IT-meeting (Graph)</strong></h3>\n<p><em>(the points marked optional can be conducted during the workshop)</em></p>\n<ol>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">a rough overview of the volume of data (Gb/TB) for the different sources that should be analyzed</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Create an AD-group of max 10-15 e-mail accounts that should be scanned (test group), e.g. \"Dataandmore_scangroup\"\n<ul>\n<li aria-level=\"2\">Make sure that all people on the list have been informed that their data will be scanned by the GDPR Toolbox and may be viewed by the project group and Data &amp; More to improve Data Classification and configuration quality<br><br></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Creation of mail sendout account (e.g. “gdprsendout_noreply@clientname.com”)</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">(optional) app registration for <a href=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/en/knowledge/rights-overview\" rel=\"noopener\">Exchange Online</a>.&nbsp;<br><br></li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Agenda</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Introduction to the participants and agree on who should be the primary contact</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Introduction to support@dataandmore.com</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Define AD group for test users</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/en/knowledge/rights-overview\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Creation and/or handover of app id and secret (app registration)</a></li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Creation and/or handover of mail sendout account (e.g. “gdprsendout_noreply@clientname.com”)</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Data &amp; More Support will configure the toolbox (10 min coffee break)</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Validation of the configuration.</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"//support.dataandmore.com/knowledge/dethrottleexchange-onprem\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">De-throttling of exchange (only for Exchange on prem)</a></li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Other sources... when and how.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"hs-callout-type-note\" data-hs-callout-type=\"note\">\n<p>Scanning of SharePoint, OneDrive, and OnPremise data sources will be the topic of the two onboarding workshop&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Next steps after the Initial IT Onboarding Workshop</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">One week scanning and review</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Client Success invites for a classification review and policy workshop (we look at data)</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Next Sources. (List of actions and responsibilities)</span>\n<ol>\n<li aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><a href=\"//support.dataandmore.com/knowledge/onpremise-data\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">On-Premise data</a> </span></li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">IT Production Meeting (after production agreement is in place)</span>\n<ul>\n<li aria-level=\"2\">Total data overview</li>\n<li aria-level=\"2\">Priority of data scanning</li>\n<li aria-level=\"2\">Certificats for domain (gdpr.client.com/dk)</li>\n<li aria-level=\"2\"><a href=\"//support.dataandmore.com/knowledge/smtp\" rel=\"noopener\">Notification mail accout</a></li>\n<li aria-level=\"2\"><a href=\"//support.dataandmore.com/knowledge/enforce_ad\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">AD verification for email</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Client Sucess Workshops to get the organization on board</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
  "sourceUrl": "https://support.dataandmore.com/en/knowledge/agenda-onboarding"
}